@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #95178 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

this is a regression caused by changes to the Windows path parsing, so a side effect ultimately caused by something this featiure not yet implemented (#94743). There is also workaround, so in the end I'd say P-medium (for the record because there's also a patch to fix this specific issue)
